<paragraph blockId="123.[157,1364,288,879]" pageId="123" pageNumber="520">few longer bristle hairs near its base, and uniformly rich brown. Braincase is long and has pronounced anterior facets. Skull is large, and I' is long hook-like. There are three unicuspids.</paragraph>
