<subSubSection pageId="123" pageNumber="520" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="123.[157,1364,288,879]" pageId="123" pageNumber="520">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[159,270,411,440]" pageId="123" pageNumber="520">Habitat.</emphasis>
Submontane and montane forests at elevations above 1450 m. Munissi’s White-toothed Shrew is not found in lower and drier forests.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
